<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>!</p>

<p>You are receiving this email because you requested a password reset for your account on HSA Tracker.</p>

<p>Please use the code below to reset your password:</p>

<p><b><%= @user.reset_password_token %></b></p>

<p>After copying the code above, please paste it in the form provided here: <a href="http://localhost:3001/reset-password/email=<%= @user.email %>">Reset Password</a></p>

<p>This code will expire in one hour.</p>

<p>If you did not request a password reset, please disregard this email.</p>
